Adeola Sowemimo bụ onye na-anya ụgbọelu Naijiria.
Ọ malitere ọrụ ụgbọ élù ya na US-based Sunrise Aviation Academy ebe ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na 2011.
N'afọ 2019, ọ ghọrọ nwanyị Naịjịrịa mbụ na-anya ụgbọelu na-arụ ọrụ maka Qatar Airways na Middle East, mpaghara nke na-esiri ụmụ nwanyị ike ịghọ onye na-anya ụgbọala.
Ọ bụkwa nwanyị Naịjịrịa mbụ na-efe ụgbọelu Boeing 787 Dreamliner maka Qatar Airways.

Ọ bụ nwanyị Naijiria mbụ na-anya ụgbọelu na-efe ụgbọelu Boeing 767 Aircraft gafee Oké Osimiri Atlantic, na-anọ n'otu egwuregwu ahụ na Captain Irene Koki nke Kenya, na Captain Amsale Gulau nke Ethiopia.
